The paper focuses on the development of artificial intelligence for autonomous driving, which falls under the intersection of computer vision (cs.CV), robotics (cs.RO), and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of sensors and their fusion, which is relevant to the field of control systems (cs.SY).
